Cell["\<\
Procedural programming explicitly specifies the steps a program should take \
to reach the desired state or output. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5629321258927317`*^9, 3.562932197825217*^9}, 
   3.5642171335978203`*^9, {3.564313840125504*^9, 3.5643138538814783`*^9}, {
