  ButtonData->"paclet://ref/FullForm"],
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " of __ (double underscore). It allows you to specify nonempty subsequences \
that contain one or more expressions with a particular pattern."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.60596717428286*^9, {3.611935960458035*^9, 3.6119359609860353`*^9}, {
   3.611936022126035*^9, 3.611936049156036*^9}, {3.6119361085360355`*^9, 
