  3.623779008174464*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"03dc2182-f421-423d-b47b-\
ea4c92e9be88"],

Cell["\<\
Not only is the functional approach easier to code, it can also make for far \
faster code.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.611938448129517*^9, 3.611938457736517*^9}, {
   3.6237792589324718`*^9, 3.623779280304608*^9}, 
